  "title": "Logistic Coordinator / Customer Service Executive #74342",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Freight Forwarder</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Logistic Coordinator / Customer Service Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Central – Marymount</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days / Mon-Fri: 8.45am - 6pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 4000 + AWS + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assist the sales department in their operations</li><li>Facilitate coordination between customers, transporters, and warehouses</li><li>Prepare necessary documentation for imports, exports, transshipments, and delivery order releases</li><li>Verify all associated costs</li><li>Respond to inquiries concerning rates, shipment tracking, and related issues</li><li>Collaborate with oversea agents and customers to guarantee seamless shipment processes</li><li></li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. O level</li><li>Min. 1 year of working experience in related role but must have experience in freight forwarding or logistics industry</li><li>Experience in handling pets/animal shipment is a plus point</li><li></li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#74342 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781<br /></p>",
